        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Amos 2:1",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", where the reference is to the Transjordanic tribes.) The Philistines subjected their enemies to a similar treatment (",
        "children": []
